						<summary>

						<p>This is damaged and dated the <hi rend="bold">18th year</hi> of the reign of the Yādava king <hi rend="bold">Rāmachandradēva,</hi> cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Sarvajitu (= A.D. 1287-88),</hi> other details being lost. It seems to record the death of <hi rend="bold">Seṁjiya-Mallaya</hi> with laurels of victory in a battle field.</p>						

